<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>GlobalConscience</title>
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Kite+One' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Alegreya+Sans+SC:900' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="fourteen columns offset-by-one">

    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <%= link_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path %>
    <% else %>
      <%= link_to "Sign in with Facebook", user_omniauth_authorize_path(:facebook) %>
    <% end %>

    <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
    <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>

      <p>By empowering individuals over centralized governments, the internet has shaken the world order. Combining geographically sourced Twitter Hashtags with the US State Department's synopses of unstable contries, Global Conscience aims to juxtapose a top-down persepctive with bottom-up reality.</p>

    <div class="seven columns alpha">
      <h3>Countries</h3>
      <form action="/country/tweet" method="get" >
        <select name="woeid" value="submit">
        <% @countries.each do |country| %>
          <option value='<%= country.woeid %>'><%= country.name %></option>
          <% end %>
        </select>
        <button>search</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="seven columns omega"> 
      <h3>Global Hotspots</h3>
      <form action="/country/display" method="get" >
        <select name="country" class="submit">
        <% @danger_countries.each do |country| %>
          <option value="<%= country.country %>"><%= country.country %></option>
        <% end %>
          </select>
        <button>search</button>
      </form>
    </div>

  </div>

    
  <%= yield %>

</div>
</body>
</html>
